Installation instructions for openBibleViewer 0.7:
---------------------------

openBibleViewer requires:

- Qt-devel >= 4.6
  or libqt-devel >= 4.6
- cmake
- clucene >= 2.3.3.4


Compile openBibleViewer:
---------------------------

tar -xjf openBibleViewer-0.7.tar.bz2
cd ~/openBibleViewer-0.7
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX='/usr' ..
make
sudo make install

